enhanced_by.reason: Setting the context is necessary to determine the compatibility of the enumeration changes.
The old schema is required to compare with the new enumeration values.
The new schema is required to update with the new enumeration values.
The isChanged method can be used to assert whether the enumeration change has been correctly applied and detected.
The getChangedElements method can be used to verify that the enumeration change is included in the list of changed elements.
